Revision history for Perl extension XTaTIK.

0.002001 2015-09-06
    - Fixed issue where pricing was global and not per-site
    - Allow setting per-region GeoIP pricing
    - Made default favicon prettier
    - Made all existing tests pass (must set RELEASE_TESTING env to run)
    - Added .cat, .subcat, and .prod classes on category list page
    - nopic.png is now properly displayed on search results and checkout
        page for products without pics
    - Added XTATIK_BLOG_SRC env var
    - Empty categories now result in 404s
    - Checking out while setting all quantities to zero
        is no longer possible (#145)

0.001002 2015-09-04
    - Mobile and IE8 fixes
    - Layout adjustments
    - Fixed 404 on checkout page terms and conditions
    - Fixed distro packaging to include proper Issues/Repo URLs
    - Fixed incorrect lookup of "fake" site/company sass bootstrap vars files

0.001001 2015-08-30
    - First DEMO release